we can create heading using the form tag.
the form tag is used to collect the user data.
in form tag there is an attribute
-> autocomplete attribute - in autocomplete when the user has saved any of the details it will show when we click on it. no need to take data manually
-> action attribute - 
-> method - 
    - get -
    - post -
-> enctype -

read only - user cant edit
disBLED - user cant even click on it
value - to display a thing on click box eg. value="hello"
box sizing - the width of page wont overflow
